MHD Handle Situations

   0 -- No MHD.
   1 -- QuasiMHD
           Storage for Bvec only necessary
   2 -- MHD with Bvec/Bn evolution
           Storage for Bvec, Bn[xyz], Bn[xyz]rhs
           Divergence cleaning if applicable
   3 -- MHD with Avec, algebraic gauge
           Storage for Bvec, Bn (eventually not),
                       Avec, Avecrhs
   4 -- MHD with Avec, Lorenz gauge
           Storage for Bvec, Bn (eventually not),
                       Avec, Avecrhs,
                       Aphi, Aphirhs



